Inner wall of penis supported with very small and irregular penial pilasters (pp). Penial verge (pv) small, cylindrical and located at distal end of penis (
Fig. 9D
).

Vagina (v) short about same length as penis and cylindricalshaped. Dart apparatus (da) very large, long and cylindrical, located at proximal end of vagina. Gametolytic sac (gs) bulbous; gametolytic duct (gd) long, cylindrical and slightly swollen near vagina. Free oviduct (fo) very short, triangular shape and entirely encircled with thick tissues. Oviduct (ov) large lobules; prostate gland (pg) runs alongside oviduct (
Fig. 9C
).
